{"lastModified":1762772548916,"uri":"c::10317073198::vessel::c3303ca0-c1af-11ee-af68-e5ba790f8393","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nAwesome performance, awe-inspiring design\n\nPrepare yourself for an extraordinarily pleasant sailing experience, aboard this 41-foot beauty, that unveils a new vision of life on board. With a hull full of power, Sun Odyssey constitutes a particularly safe choice, that benefits from sidedecks without obstacles.\n\nConsistent with the rest of the Sun Odyssey family, the model features a lower boom, which increases the sail area, while centralised winches that can be controlled directly from the cockpit, further enhance the impeccable sense of safety on board.\n\nAnd when it comes to the interior, once again it all comes down to one key principle; harmony. Staying loyal to Sun Odyssey line’s aesthetics, the design is stunningly surprising, maximising internal space, as it remains pleasantly comfortable and familiar.\n\nSearch no more. Add a touch of perfection to your sailing vacation aboard a Sun Odyssey 410.","blueprint":{"name":"ELCANO","images":["/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::c3303ca0-c1af-11ee-af68-e5ba790f8393::assets::b413e110-c1e4-11ee-b092-afed8e7f69b7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::c3303ca0-c1af-11ee-af68-e5ba790f8393::assets::f6445910-c1e5-11ee-b092-afed8e7f69b7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::c3303ca0-c1af-11ee-af68-e5ba790f8393::assets::233547f0-c1e5-11ee-b092-afed8e7f69b7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::c3303ca0-c1af-11ee-af68-e5ba790f8393::assets::23380710-c1e5-11ee-b092-afed8e7f69b7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::c3303ca0-c1af-11ee-af68-e5ba790f8393::assets::23385530-c1e5-11ee-b092-afed8e7f69b7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::c3303ca0-c1af-11ee-af68-e5ba790f8393::assets::f6440af0-c1e5-11ee-b092-afed8e7f